Escape room "The Captain’s Quarters" by Liberation Escape Rooms in Memphis
review: We had a great time! So much fun to do with a group of friends! We did the Captain's Quarters room, but will definitely be back to try the others!

room_title: Escape room "The Captain’s Quarters" by Liberation Escape Rooms in Memphis
review: Captain's Quarters was one of the better prop setups that we have been to, and my wife and I have currently been to 19 rooms and 6 or 7 different venues. Friendly staff. It wasn't high tech, but it was well set up.

room_title: Escape room "The Captain’s Quarters" by Liberation Escape Rooms in Memphis
review: So much fun. We escaped Captains Quarters and can't wait to try the other rooms.
